    <item>
      <title>随着清算量增加，比特币创下两个月来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/bitcoin-btc-extends-drop-after-one-of-crypto-s-worst-weeks-of-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在经历了 2024 年第二大周跌幅之后，加密货币市场的损失正在不断增加，这反映出对比特币交易所交易基金的需求降温以及货币政策的不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/bitcoin-btc-extends-drop-after-one-of-crypto-s-worst-weeks-of-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 04:06:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股受创，英伟达股价下跌 13%：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/asian-stocks-set-to-slip-into-cpi-election-week-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 的市值暴跌约 4,300 亿美元，引发人们猜测，推动牛市发展的行业反弹即将暂停。股市也因此失去动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/asian-stocks-set-to-slip-into-cpi-election-week-markets-wrap</guid>
